data.title: New Homes in Northlake at the Pecan Square Community
data.meta_description: Pecan Square by Hillwood is a master-planned community in Northlake, TX with new construction homes from DFW's top homebuilders.
data.text:
Discover Pecan Square by Hillwood, a community of new homes in Northlake, TX. All of the homes here are newly constructed by Dallas Fort-Worth’s best builders. New phases of development at Pecan Square offer build options in a variety of price points and home styles.

Pecan Square homeowners love being part of this award-winning lifestyle community located in Denton County, one of the fastest growing counties in Texas. Many residents here are new to Northlake, some are new to Texas, and some are living in a planned community for the first time. All are able to enjoy the benefits of a new home development where it’s easy to connect with neighbors and build new friendships in the process.

Just a short drive from two major airports and several large employment hubs, Northlake is conveniently located for commuters to Denton and nearby cities in northwestern DFW. For those who want to experience a vibrant social scene, Pecan Square is about 30 minutes from Fort Worth where thousands of entertainment options are available. Read Less
